		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">atari2600a wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'm curious, hows it the Japanese ROM but w/ a correct palette on the PAL PPU?</div>What do you mean? The palette is organized the same between the NTSC and PAL PPUs (i.e. $16 is red on both), the colors are just rendered somewhat differently due to the different video formats. The RGB PPUs used in Vs. arcade machines are the only ones with scrambled palettes.

		

